          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "92-U-238",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.998
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Transmission detector sheet",
                "consisted of five depleted uranium (DU) sheets with",
                "dimensions of 20.32 cm x  20.32 cm and thickness of",
                "0.8 mm. Behind the DU plates, 82.3 +- 0.5 g of Mn and",
                "185.1 +- 0.8 g of 99.52% enriched 11B were also",
                "positioned in the beam to serve as auxiliary flux",
                "monitors. Total mass of DU plates was 3226.7 +- 28 g."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two pairs of approximately 100% relative",
                "efficiency high-purity germanium detectors were",
                "positioned 27 cm from the intersection of the beam",
                "center and the transmission detection sheet, at an",
                "angle of 118deg relative to the centroid beam",
                "direction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRN",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The assay target was used to down-scatter",
                "incident photon beam to the energy of resonance.",
                "The assay target consisting of combination of DU and Pb",
                "was located directly downstream of the  collimator",
                "opening. The areal densities of DU for different runs",
                "varied form 0 g/cm2 (background run) to 8.47g/cm2.",
                "The Pb densities varied from 79.85g/cm2 to 86.26g/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
